text: Delicious foods and service was good. Comfortable dinning area.

the meal is so delicious and they are generous with fruits and best service ever.

The lounge is so cosy with power point for work and chilling with friends.
Was a regular here everytime and i travel and get to know the friendly staffs here, especially Richard and Mayu. Very customer oriented and feels great to go each time.
The Korean selection is REALLY AWFUL. sundubu Jigae was super oily. The side dishes and Kimchi were horrible
good food, good place, good service
